Inducing desired behavior is also the objective in [26], which attempts to respond to the  challenge of distributed AMD raised in [15]: if the same agents that seek to manipulate the system also run the mechanism, what  prevents them from deviating from the mechanism"s proposed rules to maximize their own welfare?
